---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Impact" description="1,603 datasets published, 2,896 learners trained, $2M+ in grants — quantitative outcomes from research infrastructure, open science education, and workforce development programs at UCLA and UC.">
	<h1>Impact</h1>
	<p class="intro">
		Numbers that represent real systems built, real people trained, and real research enabled.
	</p>

	<section>
		<h2>Research Infrastructure</h2>
		<ul class="metrics">
			<li>
				<strong>1,603</strong> datasets published on
				<a href="/programs/ucla-dataverse/">UCLA Dataverse</a>
			</li>
			<li><strong>54,655</strong> files archived</li>
			<li><strong>142,300+</strong> dataset downloads</li>
			<li>
				<strong>2.9 PB</strong> of data processed through
				<a href="/programs/redivis-restricted-data/">Redivis</a> in 2024
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>2 minutes</strong> —
				<a href="/case-studies/carceral-ecologies/">Carceral Ecologies</a> pipeline (down from 318
				minutes)
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			<a href="/programs/ucla-dataverse/">UCLA Dataverse</a> supports self-service data publishing
			across disciplines. <a href="/programs/redivis-restricted-data/">Redivis</a> provides a
			compliant, governed environment for restricted and sensitive datasets — P3/P4 data that had no
			institutional home before 2021.
		</p>
		<p>
			Two of UCLA's six <strong>2024 Public Impact Research Award</strong> winners were directly
			supported by <a href="/programs/ucla-data-science-center/">DSC</a> infrastructure and
			services.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Education & Training</h2>
		<ul class="metrics">
			<li>
				<strong>28 workshops</strong> delivered through
				<a href="/programs/uc-carpentries/">UC Carpentries</a>
			</li>
			<li><strong>2,896 learners</strong> reached system-wide</li>
			<li><strong>10 campuses</strong> in the UC Carpentries network</li>
			<li>
				<strong>14+</strong> open science lessons in development
				(<a href="/programs/imls-open-science-curriculum/">IMLS curriculum</a>)
			</li>
			<li><strong>500+</strong> annual learners at peak UC Carpentries scale</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Workforce Development</h2>
		<ul class="metrics">
			<li><strong>1,175</strong> documented service interactions</li>
			<li>
				<strong>190</strong> consultations handled by
				<a href="/programs/ucla-datasquad/">DataSquad</a> students (24%)
			</li>
			<li><strong>100%</strong> placement rate for a full DataSquad cohort</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Grants & Funding</h2>
		<ul class="metrics">
			<li>
				<strong>$1,850,000</strong> — Sloan Foundation,
				<a href="/programs/uc-ospo-education/">UC OSPO Network</a> (Co-PI, UCLA Lead)
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>$237,000</strong> — IMLS,
				<a href="/programs/imls-open-science-curriculum/"
					>Open Science Curriculum for Librarians</a
				> (PI)
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
	h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
	.intro { font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgb(var(--gray-dark)); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
	section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}
	section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
	.metrics {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0;
	}
	.metrics li {
		font-size: 1rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}
	.metrics li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
</style>
